{
  "stem": "1415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they worked every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I can't sing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't remember right now the words.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would have to redo it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On a different tape maybe I can-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I-- I haven't practiced that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It takes a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- like I say, it's a four-minute song, and you have to really rehearse yourself to tell the story right.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's got verses and song in the middle, and it's a song that tells the story of-- of the Jewish plight, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It takes place in a small town, and it probably was written during the First World War.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It-- it shows a small town somewhere in Poland, where-- where the Germans invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they come in to a-- to a synagogue in a small town, and it happens to be Yom Kippur, and they all say in Kol Nidre.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he comes in-- the Germans come in and the Russians on-- on the other side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and the Germans come in, and they say that they have hidden a-- an informer into the-- into the synagogue in the middle of Kol Nidre.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and the old rabbi is in awe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He-- he doesn't understand what they even mean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And here this old man finally comes forward, and he's 80 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he says he is that informer, and he dies on Kiddush HaShem on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the song goes on, and Kol Nidre continues.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And It's-- it's-- it's a little monologue story, and this is what I learned in that camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And somehow I had to revive it all the time because it's involved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I used to sing a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I used to sing a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
